{"tid":755263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【2D睇】區會新選區　4陣地大撕殺","createTime":"2018-07-25T05:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T05:35:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6053fd3497f0c60b3a18f6728d1ebf685bbf19ce","tid":755263,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:35:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180725/20459897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F20459897&d=6VBb3GZXc6PsEmgOQRdGZxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5ba25bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F20459897&h=c95854c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180725/20459897</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月25日 <br />\n<br />\n【2D睇】區會新選區　4陣地大撕殺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府公佈明年底舉行的區議會選舉新增21個議席，分散於10個不同選區，其中元朗區增加多達4席，沙田與觀塘亦各有3席進賬。新議席是兩大陣營撕殺之地，其中在4個選區，黨派旗海處處，甚至同陣營互插，《蘋果》2D為你解構。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n泛民籲一人一信反區選重新劃界<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"}]}